{"tid":1964963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宋智孝「國中學生照」出土！　頂男生頭耳上激短髮…真實顏值驚呆全場","createTime":"2020-04-09T07:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T08:00:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b29914ad31ea8eb64ca85e692359016b1f81f6e2","tid":1964963,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女星宋智孝活躍在綜藝節目《Running Man》，直率真性情相當討喜，近來錄影時，難得曝光學生時期的短髮舊照，被讚根本是從小美到大的「母胎美女」，驚人美貌也意外掀起一陣熱議。<br />\n<br />\n先前播出的《RM》中，其中一個遊戲環節，剛好聊到藝人們小時候的人氣及受歡迎程度。宋智孝除了被翻出高中時期頂著「蘇子葉頭髮」入鏡的照片，她也提到，國中時期被管得比較嚴，被規定頭髮最多只能留到耳下3公分，而她翻出的照片中，頭髮直接短到耳上位置，看起來相當俐落。<br />\n<br />\n國中舊照一曝光，宋智孝仍被形容根本是「母胎美女」，讓全場藝人一致好評大讚「好看」，一旁的金鍾國也忍不住稱讚，「那時的髮型不錯啊。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，全昭旻也翻出學生時期的照片，「我小時候好像還是滿受歡迎的。」不過，她下秒話鋒一轉，透露以前會和媽媽一起，親手做要送給男生的巧克力，卻無奈表示：「一般我喜歡的男生，都喜歡我的好朋友。」"},{"pid":"eed25d916c7c6d64249ed0f12180b0c4353757e3","tid":1964963,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4805/d4805501.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4805%2Fd4805501.jpg&h=f3d9abaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋智孝高中時期照片。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4805/d4805500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4805%2Fd4805500.jpg&h=3f73ab34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋智孝國中短髮照。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）"},{"pid":"e0fc2b7776db51410f48790bd325aa8064edde47","tid":1964963,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"c76479584f7088532e4fccafdf4bbb277f29f6c3","tid":1964963,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4805/d4805502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4805%2Fd4805502.jpg&h=7d56ac49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲全昭旻小時候也很受歡迎。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）"},{"pid":"8db1e5e601c07e1e84394068ffea526e93d3737b","tid":1964963,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"ddf75124d824660a8929d55b8be529a9dadc9f3b","tid":1964963,"uid":189109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c76479584f7088532e4fccafdf4bbb277f29f6c3","tid":1964963,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4805/d4805502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4805%2Fd4805502.jpg&h=7d56ac49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲全昭旻小時候也很受歡迎。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"同智孝冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7e11966b1ebdc99c30af4c09fa2787bb6421aa","tid":1964963,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"印度佬至愛呢種男人頭..<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1300a7f33572e3ed74582302520c1e7f96a42bb","tid":1964963,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea7e11966b1ebdc99c30af4c09fa2787bb6421aa","tid":1964963,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"印度佬至愛呢種男人頭..<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"他有輕度弱智 請見諒"},{"pid":"a048409aed9f18a03deac75ef0e8e7f0c912c2f8","tid":1964963,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1300a7f33572e3ed74582302520c1e7f96a42bb","tid":1964963,"uid":16659,"like"